# The numeric bootstrap table is a generated carrier artifact. Its bytes are
# compared directly with fk_prog embedded in form-cli-emitted.c, so checkout
# must never rewrite LF to CRLF even when core.autocrlf is enabled on Windows.
/form-stdlib/bootstrap/form-cli-table.txt -text

# The native form-cli source digest binds every Form recipe and both bootstrap
# shell scripts by exact bytes. Keep those authored sources on canonical LF on
# every host so a Windows checkout rebuilds the same carrier identity.
*.fk text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
